This paper is primarily focused on face manipulation using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of unsupervised clustering and external memory, which are common topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the behavior of the human visual system, which is relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) and graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories.
